[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`FuzzerSecurityIssueLow`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m caused by a Java `StackOverflowError` during [0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.util.regex.Pattern` methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`GroupHead.match`, `Loop.match`, [0m                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue: During fuzz testing, executing a compiled regular expression led to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded recursive calls within Java‚Äôs regex engine, exhausting the call stack and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproducing a `StackOverflowError`.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability type: Resource-exhaustion [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstack overflow[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in regular-expression [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing, reported as a low-severity finding.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observations and findings:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ‚Ä¢ The stack trace is dominated by repeated invocations of `Pattern` internal [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatch methods, indicating deep backtracking or recursion in the regex evaluator.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ‚Ä¢ The exception can be consistently reproduced by invoking the same regex logic [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munder constrained stack conditions.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ‚Ä¢ No application-specific code appears on the stack; the failure occurs entirely [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin the JDK‚Äôs regex implementation.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ‚Ä¢ The harness code merely triggers the regex routine and is not the root cause.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Areas for investigation:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m501[0m[39m:        value = [0m[1;35mvalue.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35moperator.getLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m502[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m503[0m[39m:        Boolean booleanVal = [0m[1;35mparseBoolean[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m504[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbooleanVal != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m505[0m[39m:            return new [0m[1;35mBooleanMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbooleanVal, operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m506[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m507[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m508[0m[39m:        Double doubleVal = [0m[1;35mOperandResolver.parseDouble[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m509[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoubleVal != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m510[0m[39m:            return new [0m[1;35mNumberMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoubleVal, operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m511[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m512[0m[39m:        ErrorEval ee = [0m[1;35mparseError[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m513[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mee != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m514[0m[39m:            return new [0m[1;35mErrorMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mee.getErrorCode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m515[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m516[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m517[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95melse[0m[39m - just a plain string with no interpretation.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m518[0m[39m:        return new [0m[1;35mStringMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue, operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Summary of root cause[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The Countif.StringMatcher class relies on Java‚Äôs regex engine to implement [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExcel-style wildcards [0m[1;39m([0m[39m‚Äú*‚Äù ‚Üí ‚Äú.*‚Äù, ‚Äú?‚Äù ‚Üí ‚Äú.‚Äù[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, leading to unbounded backtracking [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand eventual `StackOverflowError` for adversarial or deeply nested patterns.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There are no safeguards on pattern length or complexity, so fuzzed input can [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger catastrophic recursion in `[0m[1;35mPattern.matcher[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.matches[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High-level strategy[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Eliminate use of Java‚Äôs backtracking regex engine for wildcard matching in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCountif.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace it with a linear-time, custom wildcard-matching algorithm that [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msupports only ‚Äú*‚Äù [0m[1;39m([0m[39mzero-or-more[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and ‚Äú?‚Äù [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexactly one[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m semantics, plus [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcase-insensitive matching.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve existing operator semantics [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`=`, `<>`, default, but reject [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-equality operators for wildcard patterns exactly as before[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep all other Countif logic untouched [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumber, boolean, error predicates, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtest harness[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Changes in Countif.java[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Add helper method for wildcard matching[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Insert a `private static boolean [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString text, String [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in Countif that:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ‚Ä¢ Treats ‚Äò?‚Äô as matching any single char.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ‚Ä¢ Treats ‚Äò*‚Äô as matching any sequence of chars [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding empty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ‚Ä¢ Operates in [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn + m[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m time using two-pointer/greedy approach with [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbacktracking pointers.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ‚Ä¢ Assumes both `text` and `pattern` are already converted to the same case.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Modify StringMatcher inner class[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Remove or ignore its `Pattern _pattern` field and any invocation of [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPattern.compile[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Add fields:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          private final String _patternText;      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m original wildcard string[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          private final boolean _hasWildcards;    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m true if patternText contains [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m‚Äò*‚Äô or ‚Äò?‚Äô[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In the constructor:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Store `_patternText = [0m[1;35mvalue.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Compute `_hasWildcards = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'?'[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m>= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In the `[0m[1;35mmatches[0m[1;39m([0m[39mValueEval x[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Retrieve `String text = [0m[1;35mx.getStringValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Normalize: `String utext = [0m[1;35mtext.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Boolean matchResult = [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                _hasWildcards[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  ? [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mutext, _patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  : [0m[1;35mutext.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          ‚Ä¢ Return `[0m[1;35mevaluate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmatchResult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to honor `=`, `<>`, or default operator.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Remove import of `java.util.regex.Pattern` and any regex-related members [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom StringMatcher.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Detailed steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4.1[0m[39m. Add import:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       import java.util.Locale;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4.2[0m[39m. In Countif.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin class Countif[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After existing nested classes, before [0m[1;35mcreateCriteriaPredicate[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       private static boolean [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString text, String pattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           int t = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, p = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, starIdx = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m, backtrackT = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           int tLen = [0m[1;35mtext.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, pLen = [0m[1;35mpattern.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mt < tLen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'?'[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtext.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mt[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m match single character[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   t++; p++;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m record star position and advance pattern[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   starIdx = p++;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   backtrackT = t;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstarIdx != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m backtrack: let [0m[32m'*'[0m[39m consume one more char[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   p = starIdx + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   t = ++backtrackT;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   return false;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m skip trailing [0m[32m'*'[0m[39m in pattern[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               p++;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return p == pLen;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4.3[0m[39m. Update StringMatcher inner class:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - Remove:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           private final Pattern _pattern;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         and any calls to `[0m[1;35mgetWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - Add fields:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           private final String _patternText;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           private final boolean _hasWildcards;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - Constructor before:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           public [0m[1;35mStringMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString value, CmpOp operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[39moperator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               Pattern p = [0m[1;35mgetWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               _pattern = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp == null ? null : p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               _value = value;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         After:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           public [0m[1;35mStringMatcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString value, CmpOp operator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[39moperator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m store uppercase for case-insensitive[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               _patternText = [0m[1;35mvalue.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               _hasWildcards = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'?'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               _value = value;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m keep original for [0m[1;35mtoString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       - matches method before:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           public boolean [0m[1;35mmatches[0m[1;39m([0m[39mValueEval x[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               String text = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mStringEval[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getStringValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_pattern != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   return [0m[1;35m_pattern.matcher[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtext[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.matches[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               return [0m[1;35mtext.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_value[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         After:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           @Override[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           public boolean [0m[1;35mmatches[0m[1;39m([0m[39mValueEval x[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               String text = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mStringEval[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getStringValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               String utext = [0m[1;35mtext.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               boolean match = _hasWildcards[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   ? [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mutext, _patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   : [0m[1;35mutext.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               return [0m[1;35mevaluate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmatch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4.4[0m[39m. Leave `[0m[1;35mgetWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` intact [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit may continue to be referenced [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melsewhere[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but StringMatcher no longer uses it. No other parts of Countif are [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maffected.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The custom wildcardMatch method executes in linear time and constant stack [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspace, completely eliminating stack overflow risk.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Case-insensitive behavior is preserved by normalizing to upper case with [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Locale.ROOT`.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Equality and negation operators continue to work exactly as before; [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-equality string operators still throw IllegalStateException [0m[1;39m([0m[39msame as [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregex-based implementation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Numeric, boolean, and error predicates in Countif are untouched.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential side effects & mitigation[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure wildcardMatch correctness against existing POI unit tests for COUNTIF [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwildcards.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Validate that patterns like ‚Äúfile?name*‚Äù match ‚Äúfilename123‚Äù correctly.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Check that leading/trailing literal characters are handled.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance for very long patterns is safe [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn+m[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so even long inputs won‚Äôt[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrash or exhaust the stack.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If any unanticipated behavior change arises, adjust wildcardMatch or [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthresholds, but regex engine use is fully removed for wildcard matching.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. References[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar glob-matching logic appears in minimal HTTP path matching in other [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparts of POI; this approach centralizes wildcard logic and avoids unbounded [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No modifications to fuzz harness or external libs; tests and consumers of [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCountif will remain compatible.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            return [0m[1;35mevaluate[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mactual.compareToIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     * Matches the given text against a simple wildcard pattern.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     * Supports [0m[32m'?'[0m[39m for any single character and [0m[32m'*'[0m[39m for any sequence of [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacters.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     * Both text and pattern must be pre-normalized to the same case.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    private static boolean [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString text, String pattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        int t = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, p = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, starIdx = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m, backtrackT = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        int tLen = [0m[1;35mtext.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, pLen = [0m[1;35mpattern.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mt < tLen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'?'[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtext.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mt[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                t++; p++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                starIdx = p++;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                backtrackT = t;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstarIdx != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                p = starIdx + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                t = ++backtrackT;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                return false;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mp < pLen && [0m[1;35mpattern.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            p++;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+        return p == pLen;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m [0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     @Override[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m527[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#DIV/0!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m528[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.DIV_ZERO;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m529[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m530[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#VALUE!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m531[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.VALUE_INVALID;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m532[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m533[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#REF!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m534[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.REF_INVALID;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m535[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m536[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#NAME?"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m537[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.NAME_INVALID;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m538[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m539[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#NUM!"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m540[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.NUM_ERROR;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m541[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m542[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"#N/A"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m543[0m[39m:            return ErrorEval.NA;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m544[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m545[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m546[0m[39m:        return null;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m547[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m548[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m549[0m[39m:     * Boolean literals [0m[1;39m([0m[32m'TRUE'[0m[39m, [0m[32m'FALSE'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m treated similarly but NOT same as [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumbers.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m550[0m[39m:     * @return [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@code null[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m to represent blank values[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m551[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m552[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* package *[0m[35m/[0m[39m static Boolean [0m[1;35mparseBoolean[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString strRep[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m553[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mstrRep.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m554[0m[39m:            return null;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m555[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m556[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mswitch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mstrRep.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m557[0m[39m:            case [0m[32m't'[0m[39m:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m558[0m[39m:            case [0m[32m'T'[0m[39m:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m559[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"TRUE"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstrRep[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m560[0m[39m:                    return Boolean.TRUE;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m561[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m562[0m[39m:                break;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m563[0m[39m:            case [0m[32m'f'[0m[39m:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m564[0m[39m:            case [0m[32m'F'[0m[39m:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m565[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"FALSE"[0m[1;35m.equalsIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstrRep[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m566[0m[39m:                    return Boolean.FALSE;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m567[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m568[0m[39m:                break;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m569[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m570[0m[39m:        return null;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m571[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m572[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore original brace and nested‚Äêclass structure in Countif.java  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Revert the last patch‚Äôs removal of the existing `ErrorMatcher` and the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal `StringMatcher` class.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that after `BooleanMatcher` ends, the file continues with `public [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatic final class ErrorMatcher`, then the original `public static final class [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStringMatcher`, and that all of these nested classes close properly before the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtop‚Äêlevel `Countif` class‚Äôs closing brace.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Introduce custom wildcard matching without disturbing class scopes  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inside the existing `StringMatcher` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe one declared after `ErrorMatcher`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremove or ignore the private `Pattern _pattern` field and the call to [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPattern.matcher[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add two new private final fields to `StringMatcher`:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `String patternText` ‚Äì the upper‚Äêcased criteria text  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `boolean hasWildcards` ‚Äì true if the criteria contains `[0m[32m'*'[0m[39m` or `[0m[32m'?'[0m[39m`  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `StringMatcher` constructor, initialize these fields:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `patternText = [0m[1;35mvalue.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `hasWildcards = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mvalue.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'?'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implement the wildcard engine as a private static method in Countif  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a private helper in Countif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moutside of any nested matcher, but inside the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCountif class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m named `[0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString text, String pattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, implementing the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclassic two‚Äêpointer with backtrack algorithm:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Advance pointers when characters match or pattern has `[0m[32m'?'[0m[39m`.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Record positions when seeing `[0m[32m'*'[0m[39m` and backtrack when a later mismatch [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ After the text is consumed, skip any trailing `[0m[32m'*'[0m[39m` in the pattern.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Return true only if both pointers reach the end.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Wire up `[0m[1;35mStringMatcher.matches[0m[1;39m([0m[39mValueEval x[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to use the custom engine  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mStringMatcher.matches[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, detect `StringEval` inputs, extract `String [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mStringEval[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getStringValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` and compute `String uActual = [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mactual.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Compute `boolean matched = hasWildcards ? [0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39muActual, patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m: [0m[1;35muActual.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpatternText[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Delegate to `[0m[1;35mevaluate[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmatched[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to preserve the comparison operator logic.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For non‚Äêstring or `BlankEval` cases, preserve the existing `[0m[1;35mswitch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mgetCode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic unchanged.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Remove unused regex‚Äêbased methods or fields  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If `getWildCardPattern` and `Pattern _pattern` are no longer invoked, remove [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthem [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand their imports[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to avoid confusion and eliminate any chance of falling [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mback to `java.util.regex`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Retain the `import java.util.Locale;` introduced earlier.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verify brace balance and indentation  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After modifications, use your IDE or a simple brace‚Äêcounting script to confirm[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat every `class` or `method` opens and closes correctly.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure there is exactly one closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` for the top‚Äêlevel `public class [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCountif` at the end of the file.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Run `poi:compileJava` and existing unit tests  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness code and existing test suite should pass without change, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirming that the new wildcard logic replaces the problematic regex engine while [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving all other functionality.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- We preserve the original nested‚Äêclass hierarchy [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MatcherBase`, `NumberMatcher`, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BooleanMatcher`, `ErrorMatcher`, and `StringMatcher`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to avoid syntax errors and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaintain existing dispatch logic in `createGeneralMatchPredicate`.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By injecting the custom `wildcardMatch` helper at the class level and [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencapsulating its usage inside the existing `StringMatcher`, we avoid modifying any[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness or test code, and we eliminate the pathological regex backtracking without [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtouching external libraries.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach maintains the same public API and comparison operator semantics [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovided by `MatcherBase` while surgically replacing only the costly pattern [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatching in `StringMatcher`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removing the regex fallback [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Pattern.compile` and `_pattern.matcher`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ensures no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minadvertent use of Java‚Äôs regex engine, closing the original stack‚Äêoverflow [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerability.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Proper brace restoration addresses the compiler errors [0m[1;39m([0m[39m‚Äúillegal start of [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpression‚Äù, ‚Äú[0m[32m';'[0m[39m expected‚Äù, and ‚Äúreached end of file while parsing‚Äù[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m by returning [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe file to a well‚Äêformed Java AST before applying the new logic.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Should any unintended side‚Äêeffects arise [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., subtle differences in matching [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, they can be mitigated by adding targeted unit tests for edge‚Äêcase [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwildcard patterns [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[32m'*a?b*'[0m[39m`, empty strings, escaped wildcards, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m within the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Countif` test suite.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/31/25 00:36:56][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=339126;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=651258;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0mn evals: [1;36m3[0m, patch status: PatchStatus.UNCOMPILABLE[1m)[0m                                 [2m               [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Initial Issue  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  A Jazzer fuzzing run reported a FuzzerSecurityIssueLow due to a [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`StackOverflowError` in `java.util.regex.Pattern` while matching deeply nested or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological wildcard patterns in the `Countif.StringMatcher` code.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The team replaced all uses of `java.util.regex.Pattern` in [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Countif.StringMatcher` with a custom, iterative `wildcardMatch` function. They [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremoved the static `getWildCardPattern` method and Pattern fields, introduced [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muppercase normalization, and switched to `[0m[1;35mString.compareToIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` based on whether the criteria contained `*` or `?`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Patch Result  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The build failed with compilation errors. References to the now‚Äêremoved [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`getWildCardPattern` method in `LookupUtils.java` and `DStarRunner.java` cause [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m‚Äúcannot find symbol‚Äù errors. In addition, there is a compile error in [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`GenericRecordUtil.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchecked cast warning[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and a deprecation error around [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcell.setCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `BaseFormulaEvaluator`. The overall build for the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi` module fails.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A recursive deep‚Äêpattern match on Excel‚Äêstyle wildcards [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`*` and `?`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Countif.StringMatcher` triggered a `StackOverflowError`.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The Jazzer report showed alternating calls in `Pattern$BmpCharProperty.match`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Pattern$GroupHead.match`, `Pattern$Loop.match`, etc., indicating unbounded [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion when evaluating certain crafted inputs.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - File modified: [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/ss/formula/functions/Countif.java`.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Imports changed: dropped `import java.util.regex.Pattern;`, added `import [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjava.util.Locale;`.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `StringMatcher` fields changed from  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `_value` [0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginal criteria[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `_pattern` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe compiled regex[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `String patternText` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mupper-cased criteria[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `boolean hasWildcards`  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ `String value` [0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginal criteria[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Constructor now uppercases `value` once, sets `hasWildcards = [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mvalue.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"*"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mvalue.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"?"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mmatches[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` rewritten to:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ Handle blank cells via `value` rather than `_pattern`.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ Short-circuit mismatches on non-StringEvals.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ Uppercase the cell text for case-insensitive compare.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ For empty strings, preserve the original `=`, `<>` semantics.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ If `hasWildcards` is true, call `[0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39muActual, patternText[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ‚Ä¢ Otherwise, use `[0m[1;35mactual.compareToIgnoreCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The static `[0m[1;35mgetWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method and all uses of [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPattern.compile[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` were removed.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added a new private static `[0m[1;35mwildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString text, String pattern[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplementing a classic two‚Äêpointer wildcard matcher supporting `?` and `*`.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Result and Build Log  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
