[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore and reapply the wildcard‚Äêmatcher replacement in Countif.StringMatcher, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand update all remaining call sites [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLookupUtils and DStarRunner[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to use the new [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAPI instead of the now‚Äêremoved [0m[1;35mgetWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In LookupUtils.StringLookupComparer[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì Remove the field `_wildCardPattern` and its initialization via [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCountif.StringMatcher.getWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_value[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì Introduce a boolean `hasWildcards = [0m[1;35mlookupString.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"*"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mlookupString.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"?"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì At match time, if `hasWildcards` is true call [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCountif.StringMatcher.wildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcellValue.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mlookupString.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`; otherwise use `equalsIgnoreCase` or `startsWith` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdepending on the exact semantics of LOOKUP vs MATCH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In DStarRunner[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì Replace the call to [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCountif.StringMatcher.getWildCardPattern[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlowerCondition[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ‚Ä¢ `boolean hasWildcards = [0m[1;35mlowerCondition.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'*'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mlowerCondition.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[32m'?'[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ‚Ä¢ If `hasWildcards`, return [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCountif.StringMatcher.wildcardMatch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlowerValue, lowerCondition[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           else return `[0m[1;35mlowerValue.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlowerCondition[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix the unchecked cast in GenericRecordUtil.java:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì Change [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mm.putAll[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mMap<String,Supplier<?>>[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mbaseMap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to a two‚Äêstep, safe cast:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        @[0m[1;35mSuppressWarnings[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"unchecked"[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        Map<String,Supplier<?>> castMap = [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mMap<String,Supplier<?>>[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMap<?,?>[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mbaseMap;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mm.putAll[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcastMap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì This preserves the existing semantics, silences the warning, and avoids a raw [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mObject‚ÜíMap cast.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Adapt BaseFormulaEvaluator to the removal of [0m[1;35mCell.setCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Locate all usages of `[0m[1;35mcell.setCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in BaseFormulaEvaluator.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Replace the one‚Äêshot type switch with explicit ‚Äúset value‚Äù calls:[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì If the new cellType is BLANK: invoke `[0m[1;35mcell.setBlank[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì If STRING: invoke `[0m[1;35mcell.setCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstringResult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì If NUMERIC: invoke `[0m[1;35mcell.setCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumericResult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì If BOOLEAN: invoke `[0m[1;35mcell.setCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbooleanResult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Äì If ERROR: invoke `[0m[1;35mcell.setCellErrorValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39merrorResult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Remove all direct calls to the now-missing `setCellType`, so that [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBaseFormulaEvaluator compiles against the current Cell API.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Verify no other submodule still imports or references java.util.regex.Pattern [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor wildcard matching. Remove any stray imports.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Run a full build and regression test suite to ensure:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì All fuzz harness‚Äêtriggered wildcard tests still pass under the new iterative [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malgorithm.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì GenericRecordUtil no longer yields unchecked‚Äêcast warnings.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì BaseFormulaEvaluator compiles and its existing tests still pass.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‚Äì LookupUtils and DStarRunner behave identically for wildcard and non-wildcard [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcases.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- We preserve Countif.StringMatcher‚Äôs optimized, non-recursive wildcardMatch for [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz safety.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- We eliminate all references to the removed getWildCardPattern, bringing callers [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min line with the new API.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The unchecked‚Äêcast fix in GenericRecordUtil is minimally invasive, keeps the same[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msemantics, and localizes the suppression.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Rewriting BaseFormulaEvaluator‚Äôs type setting into explicit setXXX calls aligns [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the modern Cell API, removes the broken call, and retains existing [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformula-evaluation logic.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No harness or external dependencies are modified, and all existing public APIs [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mCountif.StringMatcher.matches, LookupUtils behavior, DStarRunner behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min place.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m258[0m[39m:     * For cells that contain formulas, their formulas are[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m259[0m[39m:     *  evaluated, and the results are saved. These cells[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m260[0m[39m:     *  remain as formula cells.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m261[0m[39m:     * For cells that do not contain formulas, no changes[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m262[0m[39m:     *  are made.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m263[0m[39m:     * This is a helpful wrapper around looping over all[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m264[0m[39m:     *  cells, and calling evaluateFormulaCell on each one.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m265[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m266[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35mevaluateAllFormulaCells[0m[1;39m([0m[39mWorkbook wb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m267[0m[39m:        FormulaEvaluator evaluator = [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mwb.getCreationHelper[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.createFormulaEvaluator[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m268[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mevaluateAllFormulaCells[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwb, evaluator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m269[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m270[0m[39m:    protected static void [0m[1;35mevaluateAllFormulaCells[0m[1;39m([0m[39mWorkbook wb, FormulaEvaluator[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mevaluator[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m271[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mfor[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint [0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i<[0m[1;35mwb.getNumberOfSheets[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m275[0m[39m:                for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell c : r[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m276[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mc.getCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == CellType.FORMULA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39misMatchFunction[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m976[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/ss/formula/BaseFormulaEvaluator.jav[0m[1;92ma:217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m227[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:     * Override if a different variation is needed, e.g. passing the evaluator [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto the cell method[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:     * @param cell The Cell to populate[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:     * @param cellType The wanted type for this Cell[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:    protected void [0m[1;35msetCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell cell, CellType cellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mnoinspection[0m[39m deprecation[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcell.setCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/ss/formula/functions/LookupUtils.jav[0m[1;92ma:976[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m977[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m976[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m977[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The compilation errors stem from mismatched or missing braces in two source [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiles after the last patch. Specifically:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In BaseFormulaEvaluator.java, the removal of the deprecated [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msetCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell, CellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method and insertion of the `BLANK` case in [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` was done without properly rebalancing the method and class [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In LookupUtils.java, the patch removed the closing brace of the abstract [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minner class `LookupValueComparerBase` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` that ended the class after [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mgetValueAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, causing its body to bleed into subsequent class declarations[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand ultimately leaving the outer class unclosed.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix for BaseFormulaEvaluator.java  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Remove the deprecated helper method `[0m[1;35msetCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell, CellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` entirely [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m223[0m[39m‚Äì[0m[1;36m226[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `[0m[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell, CellValue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, insert the `BLANK` case at the top of the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`switch`, then ensure the `switch` and method are each closed by a matching `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Do not touch the two existing `evaluateAllFormulaCells` methods or their [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplacement; ensure they remain within the class scope.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. After your edits, verify brace balance:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - One `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` at the start of `setCellValue`, matched by `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` after the switch.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - The class still ends with its final `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` after line [0m[1;36m293[0m[39m.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Concrete steps:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Delete lines:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       protected void [0m[1;35msetCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell cell, CellType cellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mnoinspection[0m[39m deprecation[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mcell.setCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the existing `setCellValue` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m231[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, modify the `switch` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       switch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcellType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           case BLANK:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mcell.setBlank[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               break;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           case BOOLEAN:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mcell.setCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcv.getBooleanValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               break;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[33m...[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           default:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected cell value type [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcellType + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Then immediately following the closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` of the switch, add one more `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclose the `setCellValue` method.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that the next code [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe two `evaluateAllFormulaCells` methods, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrides, and final `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m align correctly under the class.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fix for LookupUtils.java  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Locate the inner abstract class declaration:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       private static abstract class LookupValueComparerBase [0m[1;39m{[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[33m...[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           protected abstract CompareResult [0m[1;35mcompareSameType[0m[1;39m([0m[39mValueEval other[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m** debug *[0m[35m/[0m[39m and [0m[1;35mgetValueAsString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m were removed[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m New fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_value, lookupText, hasWildcards, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m were added here[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. After the last field declaration [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `protected final boolean [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m_isMatchFunction;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, reinsert the missing closing brace `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` to end [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LookupValueComparerBase`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Ensure a blank line or comment separates this `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` from the next `private [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatic class StringLookupComparer`, which remains nested inside the outer `public [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfinal class LookupUtils`.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. At the end of the file, verify there is exactly one `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` that closes [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LookupUtils`. If the file currently ends with two braces‚Äîthe method close and the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclass close‚Äîno further action is needed; if it ends with only the method close, add[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone more `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Other files  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - DStarRunner.java and GenericRecordUtil.java: these had no brace-related [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation errors; the changes in those files [0m[1;39m([0m[39mremoval of `Pattern` imports, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwildcardMatch calls, unchecked cast[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are syntactically correct and need no [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madjustment.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes should be made to fuzzing harness or test code.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restores syntactic correctness without altering core logic.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserves the removal of `java.util.regex.Pattern` and the introduction of [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Countif.StringMatcher.wildcardMatch`.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maintains the same public API for `evaluateAllFormulaCells` and generic [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcasting.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensures existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mformula evaluation, lookup matching[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Validation  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After applying these brace fixes, rerun `mvn clean compile` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor Gradle [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to confirm no ‚Äúclass, interface, or enum expected‚Äù or ‚Äúend of file while [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing‚Äù errors.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally run the full test suite to verify no behavioural regressions.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The initial issue is a Jazzer-detected stack overflow [1m([0m`FuzzerSecurityIssueLow`[1m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         occurring deep inside Java‚Äôs regex engine [1m([0m`java.util.regex.Pattern`[1m)[0m, triggered by [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         complex or malicious input that causes unbounded recursion in the `Pattern`         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         matcher. A patch was attempted that globally removes direct use of                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `java.util.regex.Pattern` in favor of a custom `StringMatcher.wildcardMatch`,       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         adjusts imports and helper methods in several classes [1m([0m`LookupUtils`,               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `DStarRunner`, `GenericRecordUtil`, `BaseFormulaEvaluator`[1m)[0m, and eliminates a       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         deprecated `setCellType` helper. After applying the patch, the build breaks with    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         multiple compilation errors in `BaseFormulaEvaluator.java`‚Äînotably ‚Äúclass,          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         interface, or enum expected‚Äù at lines where static methods and other members        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         seemingly ended up outside any enclosing class.                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. Initial Issue                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - A Jazzer security alert [1m([0m`FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Stack overflow`[1m)[0m was raised. [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The stack trace shows infinite recursion among `Pattern$GroupHead.match`,      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `Pattern$Loop.match`, `Pattern$GroupTail.match`, and `Pattern$Ques.match`.          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - This indicates that a malicious or pathological regex pattern caused the Java  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         regex engine to overflow the thread stack.                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. Observations from the Trace                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The recursion depth grows by repeating the same sequence of calls in the regex [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         matcher.                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The issue is reproducible with a lower thread stack size [1m([0m`-Xss921k`[1m)[0m,         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         confirming it is due to excessive recursion.                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The vulnerable code paths are in classes that rely on                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `java.util.regex.Pattern` to implement wildcard- and regex-based lookup functions.  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. Patch Attempt                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - In **LookupUtils.java**:                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Commented out `import java.util.regex.Pattern`.                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Intended to switch lookups to use `StringMatcher.wildcardMatch` instead of   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `Pattern`.                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Added new fields [1m([0m`_value`, `lookupText`, `hasWildcards`, `_matchExact`,     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `_isMatchFunction`[1m)[0m to the base comparer.                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - In **DStarRunner.java**:                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Commented out `import java.util.regex.Pattern`.                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Replaced calls to `[1;35mCountif.StringMatcher.getWildCardPattern[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m` and        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `[1;35mpattern.matcher[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m[1;35m.matches[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m` with a boolean `hasWildcards` check plus           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `[1;35mStringMatcher.wildcardMatch[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m`.                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - In **GenericRecordUtil.java**:                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Changed a raw map put-all to a cast with suppression of unchecked warnings.  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - In **BaseFormulaEvaluator.java**:                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Removed the deprecated `setCellType` helper entirely.                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Consolidated cell-value-setting logic into `[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m` and replaced  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the switch cases.                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ‚Ä¢ Inadvertently misplaced or removed braces around the class‚Äôs closing brace,  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         causing subsequent methods [1m([0m`evaluateAllFormulaCells`, `setIgnoreMissingWorkbooks`, [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         etc.[1m)[0m to be defined outside the class body.                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. Patch Result and Build Log                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - During `:poi:compileJava`, the compiler reports multiple ‚Äúclass, interface, or [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         enum expected‚Äù errors at the locations where `[1;35mevaluateAllFormulaCells[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m` and     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         other methods appear.                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - This indicates syntax errors‚Äîspecifically, methods are no longer within a      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         class or interface block due to mismatched braces in `BaseFormulaEvaluator.java`.   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The build terminates early with these [1;36m11[0m errors, preventing any further        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         compilation or packaging.                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m. Areas for Further Investigation                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - **BaseFormulaEvaluator.java**: verify the placement of opening and closing     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         braces. Ensure all methods [1m([0mstatic and instance[1m)[0m are enclosed within the            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         appropriate class or interface.                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - **Wildcard Matching Code**: audit `Countif.StringMatcher.wildcardMatch` and    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         related utilities to confirm correct behavior and coverage of previous regex        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         use-cases.                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - **LookupUtils & DStarRunner**: check for any remaining references to `Pattern` [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         or calls that expect a `Pattern` instance.                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - **Build Configuration**: confirm that no other files or imports rely on the    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         now-removed `java.util.regex.Pattern` in the targeted modules.                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis and Context  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The compilation errors all stem from mismatched braces in [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BaseFormulaEvaluator.java` around the newly refactored `[0m[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The last patch removed the old `[0m[1;35msetCellType[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand its braces[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minserted a revised `[0m[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block, but inadvertently added one too many [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclosing braces [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, causing all subsequent methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`evaluateAllFormulaCells`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`setIgnoreMissingWorkbooks`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to be outside the class scope.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other parts of the codebase are preventing compilation; the brace imbalance[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis the sole blocker.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Plan for BaseFormulaEvaluator.java  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Open `poi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/ss/formula/BaseFormulaEvaluator.java`.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Locate the end of the `[0m[1;35msetCellValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCell cell, CellValue cv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mjust [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the `default: throw ‚Ä¶;` line[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. You will see three consecutive closing braces:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            default:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalStateException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected cell value type [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcellType + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m closes switch[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m EXTRA [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcloses class prematurely[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m closes setCellValue method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mintended[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Remove the extra middle brace so that you have exactly two closing braces: [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone to close the `switch` and one to close the `setCellValue` method. The corrected[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile remains the single `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` closing the `BaseFormulaEvaluator` class.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Verify Class-Level Brace Balance  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that the class opened at line [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`public abstract class [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBaseFormulaEvaluator [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is closed only once at the very end of the file.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Count [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor use IDE/editor brace-matching[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to ensure each inner method and block[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhas matching opening/closing braces, and that no method definitions are floating [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moutside the class.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Functionality  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This fix addresses purely the syntactic imbalance without altering any logic [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor API, so existing unit tests and fuzz harnesses will continue to exercise both [0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch is minimal and surgical: it corrects only the misplaced brace [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout touching harness code, external dependencies, or other utilities.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It restores syntactic correctness while preserving the entire body of new [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There are no side-effects beyond restoring correct compilation; all previous [0m  [2m                [0m
